        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <exhotlnk document="../afcs/AFC02901.pdf" bookname="AFC">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the AFC
                        letter
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
                <para>Due to the cab mounts and the resulting cab travel, the hydraulic brake master cylinder drop hoses
                    on some 4300 and 4400 Models may come in contact with the intermediate steering shaft.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
